BIB.AUTHOR: (R.C.Barrall,J.A.Holmes,M.Silbergeld)
BIB.TITLE:
High energy neutron cross section validation and
 neutron flux spectrum using the HENRE source.
BIB.FACILITY:
High energy neutron reaction experiment (HENRE) source.
 For full description of source see Z.G.Burson,
 CEX-65.04 (1971).
BIB.DETECTOR:
(NAICR) 3 in by 3 in NaI(Tl) crystal, calibrated with
 standard sources.
BIB.CORRECTION: Corrected for effect of low-energy neutrons in spectrum
BIB.ADD-RES:
Reference also contains early values for reactions
 reported in Nucl.Phys.A, 138, 387 (1969), measured
 with an insulated-core transformer accelerator

(APRVD) Approved by author.
(TABLE) Data taken from report.
